---
DataPipeline
---

###Introduction

This job aims to do a demo of data pipeline to persist data from csv files . We replace null salary with the average salary.

###Installation

The code has been tested with spark3 hadoop 2.7 Python 3.9.2. Please install this Python version.
All required packages are listed in the _requirements.txt_ file.
To install them, the following command can be typed.
```
delete transformed_retailstore before running code

```

###Execution

To execute the job it is sufficient to launch the _data_pipeline.py_ script in the following way.
```
python3 data_pipeline.py
```

###Tests

In order run all unit tests written for the code, the following command can be typed.
```
python3 tests\test_transform.py
```
